<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī sakavaruṣaṁbulu 
<lb n="2"/>1061 <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> gu nēṇṭi śrīmadanaṁtta 
<lb n="3" break="no"/><unclear>va</unclear>rmmadēvara pravarddhamānavijaya 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>rājyasa<unclear>ṁ</unclear>vatsa<unclear>ra</unclear> 65 śrāhi tulā su 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>kla punnamayu guruvāramu 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>na vihāravāḍavīṭa śrīpā 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>damulu gaṁggasthānamu sēsina 
<lb n="8"/>yavasaramunaṁ jōḻagaṁgga 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>rāvutarājulaku vinnapamu 
<lb n="10"/>sēsi pōkarēṁggi peṇṭapānu vā 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>niyu nūṁkkāṁḍi yaina vikramāga 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>ṁggadēsiyappakiki sārakināṁḍu <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> ṭṭu 
<lb n="13" break="no"/>lō nā jītavaṭṭuna maṟaceṟvuna nitini 
<lb n="14"/>groppiṁccina ceṟvu ḍiggiṭaṁ buṭṭeṇḍu nē 
</p>

<!--<h4>Back Side.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="15" break="no"/>la yēnumāḍalu ga 
<lb n="16" break="no"/>ṭṭugoni yiṁddala śrīka 
<lb n="17" break="no"/>ṇṭhamanāyaku baṭṭināyaku 
<lb n="18"/>kommināyaku pōtināya 
<lb n="19" break="no"/>ru kāṭamanāyaku bera 
<lb n="20" break="no"/>sina vārisammadamuna niccitimi 
<lb n="21"/>yataṇḍunu niṁddala sōmīśva 
<lb n="22" break="no"/>radēvaraku nakha<supplied reason="omitted">ṁḍa</supplied>dīpamu yā 
<lb n="23" break="no"/>caṁdrārkkamunakuṁ beṭṭe dīni 
<lb n="24"/>nevvarēni vighnamu sēsirēni 
<lb n="25"/>gaṁggakaṟuta vēyi gavila 
<lb n="26" break="no"/>la vadhiyiṁccina pāpamuna 
<lb n="27" break="no"/>ṁ baḍaṁggalavāru śrī 
</p>

